{
  "stem": "12674.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Well, I-- I would have felt it if this happened to me, that-- that I'm here under false pretenses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and they were all such a tightly knit clan, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Nobody ever did anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But she wasn't one of them because she wasn't as outgoing as they were, you know, and she was-- she was very nice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I just-- I just started to establish a relationship with her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I would tell her that-- you know, I was like 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I would tell her she should use a little lipstick, and when-- when-- when she was taken from us, in a very horrible way-- we'll get to that later.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I want to start.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember-- I can tell you something about--.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So we lived our life, and it was OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And one day, you know, the-- the-- the-- in 1938 everything-- they-- they-- they-- they started to-- you know, Hitler with his business.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "In 1935 the Nuremberg laws was passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I had two uncles that lived in Germany, in eastern Germany in Leipzig, two brothers of my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But since they had Austrian passports, they were not affected by the Jewish laws, by the Nuremberg laws, because they were foreigners.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They had foreign passport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when in 1938, when finally the-- this had been going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody was-- they brought in a government that Hitler approved of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Austrian government was thinking, in the couple of years before, they had murdered the Austrian chancellor, the-- the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and things went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, in-- in March the 12th, I think it was, the 12th or the 13th of March, 1938-- it was Friday the 12th, I think, that they-- they started marching.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Austrian-- you know, to take over Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
